            <div class="content_head">
                <h1 class="qt_article_title">关注人工智能对劳动力市场的影响</h1>
                
                <div class="head_intro clear">
                    <div class="intro_left">
                        <span class="qt_published_date">2023-10-24</span>
                        <span class="qt_article_author"><font>作者：</font>吴孟非 刘凤良</span>
                        
                        <span class="qt_article_source"><font>来源：</font>中国社会科学网-中国社会科学报</span>
                    </div>
